x\in\Bbb Z_n^*\Longleftrightarrow (x,n)=1
\,\exists\,y\in\Bbb Z_n\,\,s.t.\,\,y^2=x\,
(y,n)=d\Longrightarrow n=ad\,,\,y=bd\Longrightarrow y^2=b^2d^2=x\Longrightarrow (x,n)\ge d
\,(y,n)=d=1\Longleftrightarrow y\in\Bbb Z_n^*\,
